{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GhLdfHp7s2DjgJhZeTwwpC","type":"tool_result","content":"200\t- `evaluator` depends on `agent-dispatch` (for SDK spawn) and `workflow-state` (for verdict recording)\n201\t- `circuit-breaker` depends on `workflow-state` (reads score history)\n202\t- `agent-dispatch` depends on `agent-resolver` (for compiled subagent definitions)\n203\t\n204\t## Implementation Patterns & Consistency Rules\n205\t\n206\t### Naming Patterns\n207\t\n208\t**File naming:** `kebab-case.ts` for all source files. Already established (`workflow-parser.ts`, `agent-dispatch.ts`).\n209\t\n210\t**Export naming:** `camelCase` for functions, `PascalCase` for types/interfaces, `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE` for constants.\n211\t\n212\t**YAML keys:** `snake_case` for all workflow and agent config keys (`source_access`, `max_budget_usd`).\n213\t\n214\t**Patch files:** Named `{base-name}.patch.yaml`. Always. Not `.override.yaml` or `.custom.yaml`.\n215\t\n216\t### Structure Patterns\n217\t\n218\tEach module in `src/lib/` is one file with co-located test:\n219\t```\n220\tsrc/lib/workflow-parser.ts\n221\tsrc/lib/__tests__/workflow-parser.test.ts\n222\t```\n223\t\n224\tEmbedded templates: `templates/agents/`, `templates/workflows/`.\n225\tUser-level: `~/.codeharness/agents/`, `~/.codeharness/workflows/`.\n226\tProject-level: `.codeharness/agents/`, `.codeharness/workflows/`.\n227\tNo alternative locations.\n228\t\n229\t### Format Patterns\n230\t\n231\t**Evaluator verdict:** JSON schema enforced (AD5). No alternative formats. Every AC requires `status`, `evidence.commands_run`, `evidence.output_observed`.\n232\t\n233\t**Workflow state:** YAML in `.codeharness/workflow-state.yaml`. No JSON, no SQLite, no binary.\n234\t\n235\t**Resolved configs:** In-memory only. Never written to disk.\n236\t\n237\t### Error Handling Patterns\n238\t\n239\t| Failure | Response |\n240\t|---------|----------|\n241\t| API limit | Record in state, wait and retry |\n242\t| Network failure | Record in state, retry with backoff |\n243\t| Agent timeout | Score as UNKNOWN, continue |\n244\t| Binary not found | Fatal error, halt engine |\n245\t| Missing embedded agent | Fatal error at startup |\n246\t| Malformed patch YAML | Fatal error with parse error |\n247\t| Missing user/project patch | Silently skip |\n248\t| Evaluator timeout | All UNKNOWN, counts as scored iteration |\n249\t| Invalid evaluator JSON | Retry once, then all UNKNOWN |\n250\t| Docker not running | All UNKNOWN with \"Docker not available\" finding |\n251\t\n252\t### Process Patterns\n253\t\n254\t**State writes:** After EVERY task completion. Never batch. Never defer. Crash recovery guarantee.\n255\t\n256\t**Trace ID format:** `ch-{runId}-{iteration}-{taskName}` — deterministic, greppable. Example: `ch-abc123-3-verify`.\n257\t\n258\t**Session boundary enforcement:** `session: fresh` = new Agent SDK query with no resume/continue. No session reuse optimization across tasks.\n259\t\n260\t### Enforcement Guidelines\n261\t\n262\t**All agents implementing codeharness v2 MUST:**\n263\t- Run `vitest run` before marking any module complete — 80%+ coverage\n264\t- Use Agent SDK `query()` for all agent dispatch — never `execFileSync`\n265\t- Write workflow-state.yaml after every task — never hold state only in memory\n266\t- Use `bare: true` for all programmatic agent spawns\n267\t\n268\t**Anti-Patterns:**\n269\t- Caching evaluator verdicts across iterations (each is full re-verification)\n270\t- Writing resolved configs to disk (memory-only)\n271\t- Using `child_process.spawn` for Claude CLI\n272\t- Adding shell scripts to the execution path\n273\t\n274\t## Project Structure & Boundaries\n275\t\n276\t### Complete Project Directory Structure\n277\t\n278\t```\n279\tcodeharness/\n280\t├── package.json\n281\t├── tsconfig.json\n282\t├── tsup.config.ts\n283\t├── vitest.config.ts\n284\t├── .github/workflows/release.yml\n285\t│\n286\t├── src/\n287\t│   ├── index.ts                           # CLI entry point (commander)\n288\t│   │\n289\t│   ├── commands/                           # CLI command handlers\n290\t│   │   ├── init.ts                        # REWORK — add workflow generation, strip beads\n291\t│   │   ├── run.ts                         # REWORK — use workflow-engine instead of Ralph\n292\t│   │   ├── validate.ts                    # NEW — schema validation command\n293\t│   │   ├── status.ts                      # REWORK — show workflow-state, strip beads\n294\t│   │   ├── verify.ts                      # REWORK — becomes evaluator trigger only\n295\t│   │   ├── coverage.ts                    # KEEP as-is\n296\t│   │   ├── doc-health.ts                  # KEEP as-is\n297\t│   │   ├── stack.ts                       # KEEP as-is\n298\t│   │   ├── query.ts                       # KEEP as-is (observability queries)\n299\t│   │   ├── bridge.ts                      # REWORK — strip beads, keep BMAD bridge\n300\t│   │   ├── sync.ts                        # REWORK — strip beads sync\n301\t│   │   ├── onboard.ts                     # REWORK — strip beads calls\n302\t│   │   ├── teardown.ts                    # REWORK — update for new file layout\n303\t│   │   ├── state.ts                       # REWORK — point at workflow-state.yaml\n304\t│   │   ├── retro-import.ts               # REWORK — strip beads imports\n305\t│   │   ├── github-import.ts              # REWORK — strip beads imports\n306\t│   │   ├── verify-env.ts                  # REWORK — evolve into evaluator setup\n307\t│   │   └── __tests__/\n308\t│   │\n309\t│   ├── lib/                               # Core modules\n310\t│   │   │\n311\t│   │   │  # ── NEW MODULES (v2 architecture) ──\n312\t│   │   ├── workflow-parser.ts             # YAML parse, schema validate, patch resolution\n313\t│   │   ├── agent-resolver.ts             # Agent config resolution, SDK compilation\n314\t│   │   ├── workflow-engine.ts            # Flow execution, loops, finding injection\n315\t│   │   ├── agent-dispatch.ts             # Agent SDK query(), sessions, trace IDs\n316\t│   │   ├── evaluator.ts                  # Blind evaluator workspace + spawn + verdict parsing\n317\t│   │   ├── circuit-breaker.ts            # Score-based stagnation detection (TS rewrite)\n318\t│   │   ├── workflow-state.ts             # State persistence, crash recovery (replaces state.ts)\n319\t│   │   │\n320\t│   │   │  # ── KEPT MODULES (existing, no changes) ──\n321\t│   │   ├── output.ts                      # Console output utilities\n322\t│   │   ├── stack-detect.ts               # Stack detection for init\n323\t│   │   ├── stack-path.ts                 # Docker compose and OTLP config paths\n324\t│   │   ├── docker.ts                      # Docker Compose lifecycle management\n325\t│   │   ├── otlp.ts                        # OpenTelemetry instrumentation setup\n326\t│   │   ├── scanner.ts                     # Codebase scanning\n327\t│   │   ├── scan-cache.ts                 # Scan result persistence\n328\t│   │   ├── coverage.ts                    # Coverage tool detection\n329\t│   │   ├── doc-health.ts                 # Documentation freshness checking\n330\t│   │   ├── templates.ts                   # File rendering and generation\n331\t│   │   ├── github.ts                      # GitHub CLI wrapper\n332\t│   │   ├── retro-parser.ts              # Retrospective markdown parsing\n333\t│   │   │\n334\t│   │   │  # ── REWORK MODULES (strip beads, keep core logic) ──\n335\t│   │   ├── bmad.ts                        # REWORK — strip beads gap-IDs, keep BMAD install/patch\n336\t│   │   ├── epic-generator.ts             # REWORK — strip beads gap-IDs, keep epic generation\n337\t│   │   ├── onboard-checks.ts            # REWORK — strip beads calls, keep preconditions\n338\t│   │   ├── deps.ts                        # REWORK — remove showboat/beads deps\n339\t│   │   ├── verify-env.ts                 # REWORK — evolve into evaluator workspace setup\n340\t│   │   │\n341\t│   │   └── __tests__/                     # Co-located unit tests (update with source)\n342\t│   │\n343\t│   ├── templates/                         # Code-generated templates\n344\t│   │   ├── readme.ts                      # KEEP — README generator\n345\t│   │   ├── docker-compose.ts             # KEEP — observability stack template\n346\t│   │   ├── otel-config.ts               # KEEP — OpenTelemetry config\n347\t│   │   ├── bmad-patches.ts              # KEEP — BMAD workflow patch templates\n348\t│   │   └── __tests__/\n349\t│   │\n350\t│   └── schemas/                           # JSON schemas (NEW)\n351\t│       ├── workflow.schema.json\n352\t│       ├── agent.schema.json\n353\t│       └── verdict.schema.json\n354\t│\n355\t├── templates/                             # Embedded defaults (shipped in npm)\n356\t│   ├── agents/                            # 9 agent YAMLs (8 BMAD + evaluator)\n357\t│   │   ├── dev.yaml\n358\t│   │   ├── qa.yaml\n359\t│   │   ├── architect.yaml\n360\t│   │   ├── pm.yaml\n361\t│   │   ├── sm.yaml\n362\t│   │   ├── analyst.yaml\n363\t│   │   ├── ux-designer.yaml\n364\t│   │   ├── tech-writer.yaml\n365\t│   │   └── evaluator.yaml\n366\t│   └── workflows/\n367\t│       └── default.yaml                   # Default sprint execution workflow\n368\t│\n369\t├── tests/                                 # BATS integration tests (rework for v2)\n370\t│\n371\t├── .claude-plugin/\n372\t│   └── plugin.json                        # REWORK — update hooks, remove old references\n373\t│\n374\t├── skills/                                # REWORK — update for v2 architecture\n375\t│   ├── harness-run/\n376\t│   ├── harness-status/\n377\t│   └── harness-init/\n378\t│\n379\t└── dist/                                  # Build output (tsup)\n380\t```\n381\t\n382\t### Complete File Migration Plan\n383\t\n384\t#### DELETE (40+ files)\n385\t\n386\t**Entire directories:**\n387\t- `ralph/` — 23 files (ralph.sh, drivers/, lib/, logs/, state files)\n388\t- `hooks/` — 5 files (4 bash hooks + hooks.json)\n389\t\n390\t**From `src/lib/` (7 files):**\n391\t- `beads.ts` — Beads CLI wrapper (entire beads integration removed)\n392\t- `beads-sync.ts` — Beads ↔ story sync\n393\t- `verify.ts` — 175-line proof parser (replaced by evaluator.ts)\n394\t- `verify-parser.ts` — Story AC parser (simplified into evaluator)\n395\t- `verifier-session.ts` — Black-box verifier subprocess (evolved into evaluator.ts)\n396\t- `patch-engine.ts` — Marker-based patching (replaced by workflow-parser.ts)\n397\t- `retry-state.ts` — Retry counter persistence (merged into workflow-state.ts)\n398\t- `state.ts` — Old session flags state (replaced by workflow-state.ts)\n399\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01CKEf3EfMT3thydJ11XftFt","session_id":"aeb5b1ee-06a7-4bdc-8279-6cd22d306d14","uuid":"8a87effd-ee01-454f-8792-c3ccf3815933","timestamp":"2026-04-02T10:42:12.029Z"}
